Control Statements

Three types of control statements are there namely,
1.	Sequential control statement
2.	Recursive control statement
3.	Conditional control statement

1.Sequential control statement
	In sequential control statement the process will execute in a sequence manner.
	
2.Recursive control statement
	In this statement the set of statement execute recursively for some finite number of times.

3.Conditional control statement
	In condition statement the process will flow by checking conditions.
	Depending on the condition the flow of the statements change.